snippet.title: QC:DE v2.0. All Features and Last Champion (of 2.0)
snippet.description:
New version of QC:DE releases tomorrow at 11am CST.

Are you ready for all that's new in our biggest update to this beast?


Why dont you give it a nice score in ModDB?
http://www.moddb.com/mods/quake-champions-doom-edition


-------------------------------------
All the music is part of QCDE soundtrack (separate download for in-game). If you want the tracks check out the album by Michael Markie

You can acquire the original tracks from the album here:
https://markiemusic.bandcamp.com/album/augmented


-------------------------------------
Join our discord where we announce when we're playing, and all sorts of stuff.
https://discord.gg/RN9hhmA

-------------------------------------
DBT's Twitch channel where QCDE is streamed on the regular
https://www.twitch.tv/dbthanatos/
